{
  "stem": "7938.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you-- if you are caught once, they caught you, so you had to work the whole day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you came back in the evening you got at least your meal.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But otherwise, the, the brutality was extreme.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sometimes, for instance, soldiers, they took on the street, they caught especially in the Jewish neighborhood, they caught all the people which were long beards.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they had a machine and scissors, and they cut.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they didn't cut the whole beard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They cut only half of it, and they let them go like this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was looking for some type of work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got work in the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They created something new which was a resettlement office.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We understood that the Germans wanted to resettle some people from the-- to the East, to East Poland where there was more space.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they wanted to have certain areas here for themselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they created right, right away something new.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a president and a vice-president and a board.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they it-- they called it in Polish [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that's what they-- that's what they wanted.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The reason that they created this is they're supposed to be the liaison between the population and the Germans.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whatever they wanted to order, they ordered through them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[GERMAN]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they called it Judenrat also.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- I didn't pay attention to it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was the same thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were same people, more or less, and in the same place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the resettlement office, we supposed to start giving out identification, iden-- identification card for everybody.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For everybody who had to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And according to the Germans, everybody had to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they called the women also.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For washing floors and even for carrying.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
